"       Section Editor",
"      </a>",
"      <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?33/5/33877/contributors\" id=\"se241\">",
"       Stephen S Gottlieb, MD",
"      </a>",
"     </td>",
"     <td>",
